descriptionHtml:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Alena, The Bow Goddess

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A new female Woodelf Follower!
THE Bow Expert!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
This mod adds a new Follower called Alena!
She is a Level 62 Woodelf and she\'s located in Angie\'s Camp (south of Falkreath).
She is marriageable. She got an own bow and 1000 daedric arrows.
Her specialities are: Archery, Light Armor, Sneaking, Smithing
Speechcraft and One Handed Combat.
The Bow is for the Newermind Bow Collection! so if you got that mod already 
just override the file!

Recommended:
I used echo 1162 Ancient Nord Armor for a better look!

Installation:
As usual drop all the files into your ...\\Skyrim\\Data ordner.

Deinstallation:
Delete the installed files from your ...\\Skyrim\\Data ordner.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
